{"id": "53bb1535-e3b4-4674-a135-55077be5c765", "task_id": "2c8662d8-10e3-4a0b-a756-a5cba77770a1", "path": "templates/index.html", "artifact_type": "file", "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>CYBER_LOGIN // AUTH_REQUIRED</title>\n    <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@400;700&family=Rajdhani:wght@300;500;700&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --neon-pink: #ff00ff;\n            --neon-blue: #00f3ff;\n            --dark-bg: #0a0a0c;\n            --grid-color: rgba(0, 243, 255, 0.05);\n            --form-bg: rgba(16, 16, 20, 0.9);\n        }\n\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n            font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            background-color: var(--dark-bg);\n            color: #fff;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            height: 100vh;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        /* Animated Grid Background */\n        body::before {\n            content: \"\";\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0; left: 0;\n            width: 100%; height: 100%;\n            background: \n                linear-gradient(var(--grid-color) 1px, transparent 1px),\n                linear-gradient(90deg, var(--grid-color) 1px, transparent 1px);\n            background-size: 40px 40px;\n            z-index: -2;\n            animation: grid-scroll 20s linear infinite;\n        }\n\n        @keyframes grid-scroll {\n            from { background-position: 0 0; }\n            to { background-position: 0 40px; }\n        }\n\n        /* Scanline Overlay */\n        .scanlines {\n            position: fixed;\n            top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;\n            background: linear-gradient(\n                rgba(18, 16, 16, 0) 50%, \n                rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15) 50%\n            );\n            background-size: 100% 4px;\n            z-index: 1000;\n            pointer-events: none;\n            opacity: 0.3;\n        }\n\n        .login-container {\n            width: 100%;\n            max-width: 420px;\n            padding: 50px 40px;\n            background: var(--form-bg);\n            border: 1px solid var(--neon-blue);\n            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 243, 255, 0.2), inset 0 0 15px rgba(0, 243, 255, 0.1);\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 10;\n            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);\n            clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% calc(100% - 20px), calc(100% - 20px) 100%, 0 100%);\n        }\n\n        .login-container::after {\n            content: \"\";\n            position: absolute;\n            bottom: 0; right: 0;\n            width: 40px; height: 40px;\n            background: var(--neon-pink);\n            clip-path: polygon(100% 0, 100% 100%, 0 100%);\n        }\n\n        h1 {\n            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 2rem;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            letter-spacing: 5px;\n            color: var(--neon-blue);\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        /* Glitch Effect */\n        .glitch {\n            position: relative;\n            display: inline-block;\n            width: 100%;\n        }\n\n        .glitch::before,\n        .glitch::after {\n            content: attr(data-text);\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: var(--form-bg);\n        }\n\n        .glitch::before {\n            left: 2px;\n            text-shadow: -2px 0 var(--neon-pink);\n            clip: rect(44px, 450px, 56px, 0);\n            animation: glitch-anim 4s infinite linear alternate-reverse;\n        }\n\n        .glitch::after {\n            left: -2px;\n            text-shadow: -2px 0 var(--neon-blue);\n            clip: rect(10px, 450px, 30px, 0);\n            animation: glitch-anim-2 3s infinite linear alternate-reverse;\n        }\n\n        @keyframes glitch-anim {\n            0% { clip: rect(20px, 9999px, 40px, 0); }\n            100% { clip: rect(60px, 9999px, 80px, 0); }\n        }\n\n        @keyframes glitch-anim-2 {\n            0% { clip: rect(5px, 9999px, 15px, 0); }\n            100% { clip: rect(85px, 9999px, 105px, 0); }\n        }\n\n        .form-group {\n            margin-bottom: 25px;\n        }\n\n        label {\n            display: block;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            color: var(--neon-blue);\n            font-size: 0.8rem;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n        }\n\n        input {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 14px;\n            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);\n            border: 1px solid #222;\n            color: #fff;\n            outline: none;\n            font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n            transition: all 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        input:focus {\n            border-color: var(--neon-pink);\n            box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(255, 0, 255, 0.4);\n        }\n\n        button {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 16px;\n            background: transparent;\n            border: 1px solid var(--neon-blue);\n            color: var(--neon-blue);\n            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: all 0.2s ease;\n            margin-top: 15px;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        button:hover {\n            background: var(--neon-blue);\n            color: #000;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 25px var(--neon-blue);\n        }\n\n        button:active {\n            transform: scale(0.97);\n        }\n\n        .status-msg {\n            margin-top: 25px;\n            font-size: 0.85rem;\n            text-align: center;\n            min-height: 20px;\n            font-weight: 500;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n        }\n\n        .error { color: var(--neon-pink); text-shadow: 0 0 5px var(--neon-pink); }\n        .success { color: var(--neon-blue); text-shadow: 0 0 5px var(--neon-blue); }\n\n        @media (max-width: 480px) {\n            .login-container {\n                margin: 20px;\n                padding: 30px 20px;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"scanlines\"></div>\n    \n    <div class=\"login-container\">\n        <h1 class=\"glitch\" data-text=\"NEURAL_LINK\">NEURAL_LINK</h1>\n        \n        <form id=\"loginForm\">\n            <div class=\"form-group\">\n                <label for=\"username\">Terminal ID</label>\n                <input type=\"text\" id=\"username\" name=\"username\" required autocomplete=\"off\" placeholder=\"USER_01\">\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"form-group\">\n                <label for=\"password\">Encrpytion Key</label>\n                <input type=\"password\" id=\"password\" name=\"password\" required placeholder=\"\u2022\u2022\u2022\u2022\u2022\u2022\u2022\u2022\">\n            </div>\n            \n            <button type=\"submit\" id=\"submitBtn\">Authorize Login</button>\n        </form>\n        \n        <div id=\"status\" class=\"status-msg\"></div>\n    </div>\n\n    <script>\n        const loginForm = document.getElementById('loginForm');\n        const statusDiv = document.getElementById('status');\n        const submitBtn = document.getElementById('submitBtn');\n\n        loginForm.addEventListener('submit', async (e) => {\n            e.preventDefault();\n            \n            statusDiv.textContent = \"SYNCHRONIZING NEURAL UPLINK...\";\n            statusDiv.className = \"status-msg\";\n            submitBtn.disabled = true;\n            submitBtn.style.opacity = \"0.5\";\n\n            const formData = new FormData(loginForm);\n\n            try {\n                // Sending request to the FastAPI /login endpoint\n                const response = await fetch('/login', {\n                    method: 'POST',\n                    body: formData\n                });\n\n                const data = await response.json();\n\n                if (response.ok) {\n                    statusDiv.textContent = \"[SUCCESS] \" + data.message;\n                    statusDiv.classList.add('success');\n                    document.querySelector('.login-container').style.boxShadow = '0 0 40px var(--neon-blue)';\n                } else {\n                    statusDiv.textContent = \"[FATAL_ERROR] \" + (data.detail || \"HANDSHAKE_REJECTED\");\n                    statusDiv.classList.add('error');\n                    triggerGlitchEffect();\n                }\n            } catch (err) {\n                statusDiv.textContent = \"[SIGNAL_LOSS] HOST_UNREACHABLE\";\n                statusDiv.classList.add('error');\n            } finally {\n                submitBtn.disabled = false;\n                submitBtn.style.opacity = \"1\";\n            }\n        });\n\n        function triggerGlitchEffect() {\n            const container = document.querySelector('.login-container');\n            container.style.transform = 'translateX(5px)';\n            setTimeout(() => { container.style.transform = 'translateX(-5px)'; }, 50);\n            setTimeout(() => { container.style.transform = 'translateX(0)'; }, 100);\n            \n            const body = document.body;\n            body.style.filter = \"hue-rotate(90deg) brightness(1.5)\";\n            setTimeout(() => { body.style.filter = \"none\"; }, 150);\n        }\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>", "patches": [], "metadata": {"language": "html", "framework": "static_html", "explanation": "High-fidelity cyberpunk login page featuring a custom CSS grid-background animation, CRT scanline overlay, and a 'glitch' text header. It uses a poly-clipped glassmorphism card for the UI. The Vanilla JS script communicates with the FastAPI backend using Fetch and includes visual feedback like a screen shake and color shift on authentication failure.", "dependencies": []}, "created_at": "2026-05-17 13:19:49.421198"}